      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in poor condition, and prospective buyers should read this description carefully before making a purchase decision. The exterior shows visible wear including dents, scratches, and paint fading that go beyond normal aging. The interior has significant wear with torn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require attention \u2014 expect repairs to be needed in the near term. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, wants a project car, or needs basic transportation and is comfortable with the associated risks and repair costs. It is priced accordingly to reflect its current poor condition, and no warranties or guarantees are implied. Please inspect in person before purchasing.",
