    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we are fully committed to transparency with every potential buyer. The exterior shows significant wear throughout \u2014 expect visible rust in multiple areas, several dents, and faded or peeling paint. The interior is similarly worn, with torn upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and general deterioration from age and use. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will likely require attention, and we encourage a thorough inspection before purchase. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a project car or someone seeking basic, budget-friendly transportation with the understanding that repairs may be needed. We believe in honest dealings and want you to have a clear picture of what you're purchasing.",
